name: URLSession.DelayedRequestDisposition
desc: The action to take on a delayed URL session task.

items.name: case cancel
items.desc: A disposition indicating that the task should be canceled.

items.name: case continueLoading
items.desc: A disposition indicating that the task should proceed with the original request.

items.name: case useNewRequest
items.desc: A disposition indicating that the task should use a new request to perform the network load.
